        <p>Polaris Automation is a Columbus, Ohio based engineering firm specializing in the design of industrial automation control systems. We offer a wide range of services including programmable logic controller (PLC) programming, human machine interface (HMI) programming, C++ and Visual Basic programming, web-based application development, relational database design and interface, AutoCAD and Intergraph services, control panel design and fabrication, energy services, and a variety of other automation related services.</p>
